<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Abraham's Blog</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/</link><description/><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.inshomepgup.com/categories/build-tools/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Rollup 教程 - 构建工具入门</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/rollup/%E4%B8%80%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1rollup%E7%9A%84tutorial/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/rollup/%E4%B8%80%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1rollup%E7%9A%84tutorial/</guid><description>&lt;p>rollup真的是非常重要的技能了。
&lt;img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/InsHomePgup/pic_go_img/main/Pasted%20image%2020240830171530.png"
loading="lazy"
>
光看官网的介绍的意思就是把很多小的js编译成一个大的。
如果我们写代码，那肯定是分成很多模块这样方便管理，但是打包的话，就是要把很多小块合成一个大块。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>把rollup命令全局添加进来&lt;/p>
&lt;p>我喜欢用pnpm&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pnpm add -g rollup
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>创建一个项目 rollup-start
进入项目
在src目录下创建两个文件
main.js foo.js&lt;/p>
&lt;img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/InsHomePgup/pic_go_img/main/blog/20241220104549209.png" width="50%">
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// src/main.js
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kr">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">foo&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;./foo.js&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">default&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kd">function&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">console&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">log&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">foo&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// src/foo.js
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kr">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">default&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;hello world!&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>接下去使用rollup来进行打包&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">9
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># cli执行 输出到控制台 -f format cjs(CommonJS)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">rollup src/main.js -f cjs
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 输出到文件 用cjs的规范 -o output&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">rollup src/main.js -o bundle.js -f cjs
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># src/main.js → bundle.js...&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">created bundle.js in 24ms
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>这里，起步指导说是要运行一段nodejs以后去直接执行js才能看到输出hello work
因为之前的代码里面并没有直接console log
所以加一段console log来直接node bundle.js 来看到结果
修改main.js&lt;/p></description><category>frontend</category><category>build-tools</category><category>rollup</category><category>bundler</category></item><item><title>Rollup添加typescript插件来编译ts文件</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/rollup/%E4%BA%8Crollup%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0typescript%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E6%9D%A5%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91ts%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/frontend/rollup/%E4%BA%8Crollup%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0typescript%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E6%9D%A5%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91ts%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p>在官网的教程里演示的是添加json的plugin。
那么作为举一反三的能力，我选择添加ts的plugin&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="rollupplugin-typescript">@rollup/plugin-typescript
&lt;/h1>&lt;p>不知道怎么上手，那我先安装这个包试试。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pnpm add @rollup/plugin-typescript --save-dev
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/InsHomePgup/pic_go_img/main/Pasted%20image%2020240830175050.png"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>根据npm上的介绍，还需要安装这两个包。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pnpm add typescript tslib -S -D
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>然后配置文件添加plugin的配置&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-js" data-lang="js">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">typescript&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;@rollup/plugin-typescript&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">default&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">input&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;src/main.js&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1">// 入口
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">output&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1">// 出口
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">file&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;bundle.js&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">format&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;cjs&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1">// 打包规范
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">plugins&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">typescript&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()]&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">};&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>npm 的介绍上说使用行内的写tsconfig的方法，我想了一下还是用文件的形式。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>根目录创建tsconfig.json 文件
然后简单写入一些基础配置&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// tsconfig.json 之前测试ts的时候的配置，随便加进来的
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;compilerOptions&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;module&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;NodeNext&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;moduleResolution&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;NodeNext&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;resolvePackageJsonExports&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">true&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;resolveJsonModule&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">true&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;allowImportingTsExtensions&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">true&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>同时去修改rollup的config&lt;/p></description><category>frontend</category><category>build-tools</category></item></channel></rss>